value.0: A rickety ladder gives access to a heavy iron-bound trap door above.
A grate set into the floor, made of wood and reinforced with thick bands of rusted iron. A noisome odour wafts up from below.
A heavy lever is mounted on a swivel mechanism, no doubt controlling the nearby trap door.
